                <div class="how-node" aria-hidden="true"><span>7</span></div>
                <div class="how-content">
                    <h3 class="text-l bold my-0">Secure Home Delivery</h3>
                    <p class="text-s opacity-90">
                    Originals are couriered safely across India with <strong>tracking</strong> and
                    <strong>insurance coverage</strong> in tamper-evident packaging.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>

        <!-- Minimal contextual internal links -->
        <div class="max-w-featured w-100p mx-auto ta-center mt-1" role="navigation" aria-label="Explore related services and resources">
            <p class="text-s opacity-80">
            Explore related:
            <Anchor href="/services/education-documents-apostille/" className="td-none underline focus-vis-outline" title="Education document apostille services">Education</Anchor>,
            <Anchor href="/services/business-documents-apostille/" className="td-none underline focus-vis-outline" title="Business document apostille services">Business</Anchor>,
