                <ul class="flex-col gap-05 text-s opacity-90">
                <li>Full page, color, high-resolution (PDF/JPG). Avoid crops/blur.</li>
                <li>Will arrange pickup if needed.</li>
                <li>e-Apostille works great with clean scans; we'll confirm eligibility.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            </li>

